<tr id="L16"><td><a href="#L16">16</a></td><td>GARAK:  But that's exactly the point, Doctor. The repetitive epic is the most elegant form of Cardassian literature, and The Never-Ending Sacrifice is it's greatest achievement.</td></tr>

